.row
  .span8.offset2
    %h2.center What is bitBIO?
    %br
    %p.center
      An online
      %strong science community
      and resource built by researchers and service providers in the life science industries. Whether
      you are seeking a service provider, collaborating on research,
      or looking for assistance, bitBIO can help.
    %br
    %p.center{style: "margin-top:10px;"}
      Gain instant
      %strong access
      to new resources, providers, and equipment
      you may have otherwise not found, and exchange science research projects or services 
      with hospitals, universities, research institutes,
      or other service providers across the globe.
    %br
    %p.center{style: "margin-top:10px;"}
      Find out what scientific methods other researchers or service providers are using.
      %strong Search for projects
      to exchange science advice, opinions, and services.
    %br
    %p.center{style: "margin-top:10px;"}
      Learn about new research, methods, and technologies to use for your project and what the science
      market has to offer. Quickly
      %strong promote research
      questions and answers
      in the science community to help a fellow colleague.
    %br
    %p.center{style: "margin-top:10px;"}
      Why rely on expensive services to broker your science project when all you really need is 
      access, exposure, and some help from the science community.
%br
